{{infobox referendum
| name         = Referendum on Stuttgart 21
| country      = Baden-Württemberg
| date         = {{start date|2011|11|27|df=y}}
| title        = Do you agree to the bill "Act on the Exercise of Termination Rights in Contractual Agreements for the Stuttgart 21 Railway Project (S 21 Termination Act)"?
| yes          = 1,507,961
